QuestData.Title: The Leaf-Reader
QuestData.Description: Good ta see you again, mon!$B$BDe Cenarion Circle sent Zen'kiki out here ta find some more of dem plants. We not likin' what we be seein' here.$B$BIf ya find any more of dem leaves, bring one on back. Dey can see right through Zen'kiki's tree disguise, even when he plant himself in da ground!$B$BAnd dat make it harder to run!
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect a Strangely-Glowing Frond from Everbloom.
